    {
      "title": "[正面] Well crafted and enjoyable character & deckbuildin...",
      "summary": "Well crafted and enjoyable character & deckbuilding roguelite that hits every mark. High quality art and music, with a fantastic Lovecraft-inspired story. Card games rarely draw me in mechanically, but check my hours to see how that went this time. \n\nMost of the game has a proper English translation now, so it's even more accessible. It will be fully translated sometime this year. Despite being a gacha game, it may even convince people who hate gacha due to the high rates on acquiring characters as well as the endless sea of currency you're given.\n\n9.2/10",
